          You may not resell, redistribute, modify, or reverse engineer Echolia, and you may not present it as your own product.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-text-main">
          2. Your content
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          You own the content you create in Echolia. Your thoughts, notes, and files are yours. We do not claim ownership over your content.
        </p>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          You are responsible for backing up anything important and for complying with any laws that apply to the content you create.
