      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-text-main">
          3. Acceptable use
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          Do not use Echolia for illegal activities, harm, abuse, or spam. 
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-text-main">
          4. No warranty
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          Echolia is provided “as is”, without any guarantees that it will be bug-free, available at all times, or work on every device or configuration.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-text-main">
          5. Limitation of liability
