        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          To the fullest extent allowed by law, we are not liable for any loss of data, loss of profits, or other damages that result from using or being unable to use Echolia. Use the app at your own risk.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-text-main">
          6. Changes
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          We may update these terms as Echolia evolves. When we do, we will update the “Last updated” date above. If you continue using the app after changes take effect, that means you accept the new terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-text-main">
          7. Contact
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          If you have questions about these terms, you can reach us at
          <a href="mailto:ping@echolia.com" class="text-accent-pink hover:text-accent-cyan transition-colors underline">
            ping@echolia.com
          </a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>
  </div>
</Base>
